## Hard rules (always)

- Astro 6 static output; no SSR unless explicitly requested.
- Romanian copy by default.
- Mobile-first. `Rezerva acum` CTA visible in the first viewport on a 360 px phone, plus sticky bottom bar.
- No phone as a primary CTA. No autoplay with sound. No client-only rendering for booking-relevant content.
- All images through `npm run optimize:images` before commit.
- Single source of truth for NAP (name / address / phone) — never hardcode twice.
- Performance: mobile LCP < 2.0 s, INP < 200 ms, CLS < 0.05.
- Accessibility: WCAG AA body text, AAA on the booking CTA.
